      "message": "nit: \n\nwouldn\u0027t it be easier to have\n\n  if opts.Buffer.MaxLeases \u003d 0 {\n    opts.Buffer.MaxLeases \u003d DefaultAUMaxLease\n  }\n\nin https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/infra/luci/luci-go/+/2382470/6/resultdb/sink/artifact_channel.go#b24\n?\n\nThen the logic would be more consolidated (in one place), and that code wouldn\u0027t have to assume that cfg.AUMaxLeases isn\u0027t 0",
