      "message": "I\u0027m not sure if I understood you comment correctly. ServerConfig{} needs a dedicated field so that users can specify the value in ServerConfig{} via NewServer(). Are you proposing that\n- SetDefaultValues() copies the value of ServerConfig.AUMaxLease to ArtifactChannel.opts.Buffer.MaxLease, and\n- artifact_channel.go#b24 assigns the default value to Buffer.MaxLeases conditionally?",
