      "writtenOn": "2020-08-31T17:03:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see you point. However, cfg.Address and cfg.AuthToken are used in multiple places. Start(), Export(), and warmup(), and newSinkServer()\n\nIt\u0027s probably OK for each of them to check and use the default value for cfg.Address, but it\u0027s not OK for AuthToken, and Run() needs to pass the generated token to each of them.\n\nI could have the default value assignment in Run(), but the current implementation looks simpler to me, because it doesn\u0027t have to pass the values to the functions.",
      "parentUuid": "5988a44e_7dd69b84",
